{"tid":211043,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"請問這裡有無負責人","createTime":"2017-04-21T11:01:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-21T11:16:36.000Z","uid":14716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1a5ac5559af0508bfea941f55cd544ad7361c5ed","tid":211043,"uid":14716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T11:01:22.000Z","msg":"請問這裡有無負責人，為什麼這裡有這麼多限制級、成人影片，卻沒有種子<br />\n而沒人監管或移到成人版，<br />\n本來我讓小朋友來貴壇，是嚴禁到成人區，<br />\n以為就此沒問題。<br />\n怎知道他們來到這裡，看到了那些限制級影片而無法下載，<br />\n變得心理開始有問題。<br />\n請趕快妥善處理，否則，我向相關部門投訴。"},{"pid":"2cebc712d29757ce745384f4cb56bf996a3497ab","tid":211043,"uid":14716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T11:16:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}